Product name: Sensitive Skin Probiotic Deodorant - with Magnesium - Natural & Handcrafted
Description:
New & Improved! Our popular deodorant formula just got even better - with Magnesium oil! Magnesium is a necessary mineral that many people, in our modern society, are deficient in. Magnesium not only plays an important role in our health and well-being, but it also is a powerful deodorizer. One of the best ways to absorb this mineral is through the skin so applying it with your daily deodorant is a win-win for everyone. 
Are you sick of commercial "natural" deodorants that just aren't doing their job and still have some questionable ingredients? 
Do you want something that not only works but is actually GOOD for you?
Probiotic Deodorants WORK - here's how: 
Probiotics are good bacteria that people usually ingest to help regulate their digestive health. Now, people are discovering that probiotics are also great at regulating the balance of bacteria on the skin. This good bacteria discourages the growth of unfriendly or harmful bacteria and yeasts such as Candida. Less bad bacteria under those arms means less odor to fight!
This listing is for 1 - 0.75oz twist-up tube of Emily's Homestead Sensitive Skin Probiotic Deodorant. For those with very sensitive skin, here's the original Probiotic Deodorant with the essential oils and baking soda omitted.  It does not need refrigeration and one tube usually lasts between 1-2 months. 
Ingredients: Beeswax, Shea Butter, Avocado Oil, Sunflower Oil, Arrowroot Powder, Shelf-stable probiotics (that include lactobacillus and bifidobacteria), Magnesium Oil, and Vitamin E oil.
Although this is unscented, it has a natural slight cocoa scent from the cocoa butter that is quite yummy!

Product name: Tallow / 5# Pure Grass Fed Beef Tallow - Organic Sourced , Rendered , Premium Quality. Five pounds of tallow in vacuum sealed pouches.
Description:
Pure grass fed beef tallow, rendered and packed in vacuum sealed bags. Five pounds of tallow packed in two Foodsaver Pouches (2.5 lb per pouch) are easy to store, lay flat to save space and are the most economical to ship! 
Unsurpassed quality- waxy, near odorless and pale. Pure Rendered Premium Tallow from the kidney fat (suet) of Certified Organic Grass Fed Beef is the only tallow we offer. Perfect For Cooking; Soap Making; Candle Making or Hand Made Cosmetics. The tallow can be gently heated right in the pouch and poured out to measure. 
Our Pure Beef Tallow has not been bleached, deodorized, hydrogenated or altered. It's 100% pure, nothing added. It's Clean, It's Safe, It's Guaranteed.
Rest assured that our production environment is free of Tobacco, Pets, Hard Liquor, Offensive Odors, Dirty Jokes and Racey Undergarments.
Pure Tallow, rendered in a pure atmosphere.
We render in a fully inspected and approved commercial kitchen, assuring product purity, cleanliness and food packaging compliance. We produce according to food safety HACCP protocol resulting in a zero-moisture / zero bacteria (shelf stable over 60°F).
Contact us if you're interested in larger quantity, we have a steady supply available.
Is the Tallow organic? Where does it come from?
The family farms that supply the suet we use are all are members of the "Organic Valley Farmers Co-op" and produce only Certified Organic Livestock, raised without antibiotics, synthetic hormones or pesticide exposure. They are seasonally grazed and not given feed containing genetically modified organisms (GMO). Organic Valley Co-op Farms are 3rd party "Certified Organic" and follow federal guidelines. The livestock processor we use is "Animal Welfare" Certified.
Effective 08/05/2015
Our fat is now rendered from only grain free stock.
